meta.name: Jeopardy!
meta.description: Jeopardy! is a classic game show -- with a twist. The answers are given first, and the contestants supply the questions. Three contestants, including the previous show's champion, compete in six categories and in three rounds (with each round's "answers" being worth more prize money).

Pat Sajak hosted Jeopardy for this episode and Alex Trebek hosted Wheel of Fortune. This is the only time Alex ever had a guest host during his run hosting Jeopardy.
